=======================================
Offline Polar features extraction
=======================================

- Compilation
$ make

---------------------------------------

- Usage:
$ ./offpolarfeat 
Usage: ./offpolarfeat image.pgm rad dis ang [-vr]

---------------------------------------

- Example: features extraction using a shape descriptor of radius 20
           with 3 distances and 8 angles

$ ./offpolarfeat pi.pgm 20 3 8 > pi.fea

- Example: features extraction using a shape descriptor of radius 20
           with 3 distances, 8 angles and vertical repositioning

$ ./offpolarfeat pi.pgm 20 3 8 -vr > pi.vr.fea

  *Note that you might want to project each feature vector using PCA
